'''Anezwu amezzay agrawan''' neɣ d talmest n [[anezwu]] yeṭṭafaren [[anezwu amezzay]], Azamul-is deg [[asesmel anezway n Köppen|usesmel anezway n Köppen]]: '''Am'''.

Isig n weẓɣal ayyuran n unezwu-ayi yugar 18° C, yegber seg snat n [[tasemhuyt|tsemhuyin]] yiwet d tanaɣurt tayedṭ d tagrawant. Dɣa di tsemhuyt n unaɣur yetteɣlay-d fellas ddaw n 60 mm n [[Ageffur|ugeffur]] kan.

== Asedger ==
Anezwu amezzay agrawan yettili deg yideggan yellan gar n ijeṛdan n tehri 5° ɣer 30° deg wamur n unẓul d unẓul-asemran n [[Asya]], akken i yella (cwiya) di [[Tafriqt|Tferka]] ([[ataram n Tferka|ataram]] d [[Talemmast n Tefriqt|tlemmast n Tferka]]), [[Tamrikt n Wenẓul|unẓul]] d [[Tamrikt Talemmast|tlemmast n Temrikt]], akken iyla (yesɛa) kra n tgezmiwin deg [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Temrikt n Ugafa]] d ugafa n [[Ustṛalya]].

